# Privacy Policy for SleepHabit

Last updated: 2/7/2025

## Introduction
SleepHabit is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information.

## Data Collection and Storage
- All data is stored locally on your device
- No personal information is collected or transmitted
- No registration or account required
- No analytics or tracking systems

## Data Usage
- Sleep records are stored only on your device
- Notes and achievements are kept locally
- No data is shared with third parties

## Permissions
- Notifications: Used only for sleep and wake-up reminders (optional)
- No other system permissions required

## Data Security
- All data remains on your device
- No cloud storage or sync features
- No internet connection required

## Children's Privacy
- Our app is suitable for users of all ages
- We do not knowingly collect data from children

## Changes to This Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Please review this page periodically.

## Contact Us
If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: [您的邮箱]
